{"title":"雪山路","authors":["刘立云"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘立云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，昨天的道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同昨天的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已被沉沉飘落的雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厚厚地严严地盖覆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史已翻开一页洁白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我用脚板去阅读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在山脚久久盘桓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一只迷途的羔羊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩乱一片迷途的痛苦——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯首，不见熟稔的脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头，不见路碑高竖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至再也找不着向导"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天曾带过路的那位大叔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已同那洁白如练的雪路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋进了深深的雪谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我执意要前行了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执意要用自己的脚板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去踩一条属于今天的通途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山呵，我知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道我的每一只脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不该是前人的重复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我背负着沉重的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正深一脚浅一脚地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着岁月的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一座峰岭走去……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}